          "title": "AI Citation Format",
          "instructions": "Students must use this format for AI citations:",
          "template": {
            "format": "AI Assistance Statement:\nI used [AI Tool Name] on [Date] for [Specific Purpose].\nThe AI helped me [Specific Contribution].\nAll written work and analysis are my own.",
